   - Custom CSS transitions are added for fade-in (overlay) and scale-up (modal content) effects when the modal opens/closes.
   - A hover scale effect is applied to the close button, and a bounce animation is added to the trigger button for interactivity.
   - The modal is styled with a clean, professional look using rounded corners, shadows, and a centered layout.

